ellite\nluminosity, and explicitly obtain such values for the Solitary Local dwarfs\nsurvey. Uncertainties in abundance matching and reionization models are large,\nimplying that comprehensive searches could lead to refinements of both models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2016 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2016 22:18:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Mar 2017 03:33:47 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 4 Sep 2017 19:40:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-06"}
