ort for the alternative \"stalled infalling perturber\" core-formation\nscenario, in which this galaxy's core could have been excavated by the action\nof an infalling massive perturber.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2016 00:03:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-05"}
