\naccuracy, which is an expected statistical uncertainty in upcoming wide-field\ngalaxy surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2016 04:44:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2016 04:09:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
