 and interfaces, such as that between a\nTI and a magnetic material, where exotic new states of matter are predicted to\nexist.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2016 07:06:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-05"}
