tions are\ngiven to illustrate these phenomena.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2016 13:29:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Jul 2017 11:34:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-27"}
