ty. It may be used to identify the cluster content in\nfuture X-ray catalogues from XMM-Newton and eventually from eROSITA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2016 13:38:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
